Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.08,0:05:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.76,0:05:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.00,0:06:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.02,0:06:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,会是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.52,0:06:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,水母
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.68,0:06:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.56,0:06:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,另一家水族馆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.14,0:07:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,请给我一张成人票
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.62,0:07:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,1350円
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.36,0:07:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.88,0:07:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,又来？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.58,0:07:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,小光你想干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.08,0:07:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这次又是哪里
